---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/band/PageHero.astro';
import FeatureRow from '../../components/band/FeatureRow.astro';
import CtaBand from '../../components/band/CtaBand.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../lib/site';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Mission & Vision"
  description="The verbatim mission, vision, and founding convictions of Favor International."
>
  <PageHero
    label="Mission & Vision"
    title="Transformed Hearts Transform Nations"
    promise="Favor International serves and trains indigenous African leaders to advance the Gospel into the unreached."
    image="/images/hero-prayer-recent.jpg"
    imageAlt="A Favor prayer gathering"
  />

  <section class="band band--white">
    <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <p class="label">Our vision</p>
      <h2 class="vision">{SITE.vision}</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FeatureRow
    image="/images/hero-pastor-preaching.jpg"
    imageAlt="An indigenous pastor preaching in the field"
    eyebrow="Our mission"
    layout="image-right"
    background="cream"
  >
    <p class="mission-body">{SITE.mission}</p>
  </FeatureRow>

  <FeatureRow
    image="/images/hero-congo-grads.jpg"
    imageAlt="Graduates celebrating in DR Congo"
    heading="A spiritual army from the broken, lost, and impoverished."
    layout="image-left"
    background="white"
  >
    <p>
      God has raised Favor up to mobilize a spiritual army from the broken, lost, and
      impoverished in 10+ countries. This army will raise up the next generation of soldiers
      growing and expanding the Kingdom of God that will overcome the strongholds of darkness
      that have long plagued Northern Africa.
    </p>
    <p class="emphasis">
      Favor International serves to transform war-torn victims into purpose-driven Christian
      victors, equipped to advance the Gospel in villages and mobilized to advance the Kingdom
      in nations.
    </p>
    <p>
      We see trauma resolved, communities revitalized, at-risk children rescued from
      traffickers, poverty shrinking, and darkness driven away by the power of the Gospel in
      action.
    </p>
    <p class="emphasis">
      Favor does whatever is needed to bring the Gospel and discipleship to unreached areas.
      Often what others are unwilling or unable to do.
    </p>
  </FeatureRow>

  <FeatureRow
    image="/images/about-leadership-training.jpg"
    imageAlt="A Favor leadership training session"
    heading="National leaders, on the front lines."
    layout="image-right"
    background="cream"
  >
    <p class="lede">
      Our passion is to mobilize national leaders in front-line battlegrounds to align their
      communities with the purposes of God in every aspect of life.
    </p>
    <p>
      National leaders are solving problems others haven't been able to. They are willing to
      work harder, more self-sacrificially, and more effectively for their people and nation
      than we ever could. Our work is to serve and train them and ensure they have everything
      they need to multiply and accelerate individual and national transformation. National
      leadership is one of our core principles in Favor.
    </p>
  </FeatureRow>

  <section class="band band--white">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2>What we instill in the leaders we train</h2>
      <ul class="trait-list">
        <li>Strong prayer life</li>
        <li>Humble dependency and submission to God</li>
        <li>Passion for the Kingdom mission</li>
        <li>Focused study of God's Word</li>
        <li>Discipleship</li>
        <li>Desire to serve native to their location</li>
        <li>Developed vision, calling, and gifts from God</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Transformation takes time and commitment. Investing in national leadership and
        discipleship has proven to be the most fruitful way to administer transformation. Our
        ministry is committed to not just give temporary relief and then leave. We are here to
        sow for a lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band band--green-deep gospel-band">
    <div class="gospel-band__photo" style="background-image: url(/images/evangelism-discipleship.jpg);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="gospel-band__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container container--narrow gospel-band__inner">
      <p class="label label--inverse">The Gospel comes first</p>
      <p class="emphasis-bright">
        Favor gets the Gospel out to unreached areas where few others go, and we lead
        discipleship efforts beyond mere evangelism to produce fruit that multiplies.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Gospel is foundational to all other humanitarian work (education, orphanages,
        business, medical, etc.) and must be in place for other organizations to effectively do
        their work. National leaders can better access all spheres of their societies with
        greater speed and less expense than western missionaries.
      </p>
      <p class="emphasis-bright">
        Favor's vision is to see national leaders of all walks of life, equipped by the rest of
        the body of Christ, establish national leaders of all walks of life to disciple other
        national leaders, to further establish the Kingdom of God.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    heading="Stand with the mission."
    body="Becoming a Favor Partner is the simplest way to put this mission into motion every month."
    ctaLabel="Become a Favor Partner"
    ctaHref="/give/partner-monthly/"
    variant="gold"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .vision {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem);
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .mission-body {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .emphasis {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .emphasis-bright {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Gospel band: real field photo behind a green scrim, matching the
     homepage's photo-behind-green treatment. */
  .gospel-band { position: relative; overflow: hidden; isolation: isolate; color: var(--color-white); }
  .gospel-band__photo { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; background-size: cover; background-position: center; }
  .gospel-band__scrim {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(31,58,26,0.92) 0%, rgba(31,58,26,0.86) 100%);
  }
  .gospel-band__inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .gospel-band p { color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-white) 88%, transparent); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); line-height: 1.6; }

  .trait-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-8); display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-3); }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .trait-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .trait-list li {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
